Mission.Title: Op_Sand_Scorpion_-_Part_8_v1.0
Mission.Comments:
The initial strike on Russian forces in Syria has shad an impact. Russian forces retreated all air assets to Jira and abondoned Alleppo and Kuweires.
They also have increased their IADS effectiveness by switching Syrian personnel for Russian.
For this followup strike we are seeking to push Russia farther East and eventually force them out of Syria. To accomplish this we have 3 missions for this stage of the op.
The 3 objectives are:
Destroy Allepo Airfield ========================= Prevent the use of this airfield for any Russian counter offensive.
Destroy Russian PMC laying seige to town ============================== The Wagner group has a town east of Minakh surrounded and laying seige to it. Conditions are worsening so the decision has been made to send a message to Russian assets of all kinds.
Capture Russian Helo FARP =========================== Capture a helo base within Syria to create a launch point for a new ground phase of the war.
